Package fr.pyvain.websight.websight.Geometry

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CPoint
    A class that represents a 2-dimensional point with constant integer coordinates.
    Event
    A class that represents an event, which is either the left endpoint or the right endpoint of a Segment.
    InterComputer
    A class containing tools to help generating graph drawings with reduced number of crossings.
    Intersection
    A class that represents an intersection between 2 or more Segment objects at a given CPoint.
    IntersectionSet
    A class that represents a set of intersections, with O(log(N)) time access to all the intersections at a given x-coordinate, or to an intersection at a given location.
    Segment
    A class that represents a 2-dimensional segment.
